{"tid":2062361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正反對立場新聞登澳門人在英國反港文章","createTime":"2020-06-13T05:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T04:51:30.000Z","uid":267970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9591ca26edf501bae773923fb96c088a5dc52946","tid":2062361,"uid":267970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:41:06.000Z","msg":"澳門人在英國呢條垃圾次次出文都唱衰BNO，又成日屈英國唔支持香港人，唔支持勇武手足，我真係好睇唔過眼呢隻賤種行為！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條友拎住本葡國護照死去英國好威？咁就可以發文踩香港人？<br />\n<br />\n我亦唔明點解立場新聞仲會容許呢條間諜登文分化英國同手足！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最新罪行：</span></strong></span><br />\n暗示英國會同勇武手足割蓆，散播失敗論<br />\n<br />\n「若果英國政府與勇武割蓆，那麼曾參與勇武行動的手足面臨包括暴動罪的檢控時，能否向英國申請政治庇護？又或者如果當中有BNO持有人的話，英國會否與之割蓆？」<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/香港半年報告-英國與勇武割蓆/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%87%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E5%89%B2%E8%93%86%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=e2f796f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%87%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E5%89%B2%E8%93%86%2F&h=5c103715\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/香港半年報告-英國與勇武割蓆/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罪行2:</span></strong></span><br />\n散播英國唔會接收香港人既信息，斷抗爭者後路<br />\n<br />\n「最後，亦是令人覺得最吊詭的，是約翰遜文章的結尾。他稱，英國希望香港在「一國兩制」之下成功，並呼籲中英共同合作將之實現。是否暗示只要中國叫停「港區國安法」，英國就會叫停接收港人的計劃？」<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/bno-平權-working-holiday-2-0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2Fbno-%E5%B9%B3%E6%AC%8A-working-holiday-2-0%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=b84d06f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2Fbno-%E5%B9%B3%E6%AC%8A-working-holiday-2-0%2F&h=e6ba5cf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/bno-平權-working-holiday-2-0/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罪行3: </span></strong></span><br />\n2019年10月亂屈肥彭唔提BNO平權，再加屈香港人只想拎利益，無國家會幫香港人<br />\n<br />\n「彭定康曾於訪港時承諾劉慧卿會於上議院提出 BNO 平權，但在此動議辯論中完全沒有提及為 BNO 平權，爭取居英權等的內容；其實早前彭定康亦缺席 Hong Kong Watch 有關 BNO 平權的座談會，究竟是貴人事忙，還是另有原因，耐人尋味。」<br />\n<br />\n「我想要你地個國籍，但你放心，香港冇事的話我唔會嚟，我只係想有咩冬瓜豆腐可以走嚟你地度。」試問這樣的邏輯，真的能說服有國家伸出援手嗎？<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/對促英聯邦國家予港人第二國籍的思考/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%AF%E9%82%A6%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%88%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=07444ba9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%AF%E9%82%A6%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%88%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%2F&h=cbf4a16e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/對促英聯邦國家予港人第二國籍的思考/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國澳門人無一個係好人</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>立場新聞你幾時先肯ban左條友？</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3a765b4ace443d69fbde7dd3369487210fe17e43","tid":2062361,"uid":8984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356937786cdd9c60ac06ef751dd1bfbe39c10eaf","tid":2062361,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"你投稿去反駁佢囉"},{"pid":"3a436c69b3155ebae4c61bd9e0f2953d427fe429","tid":2062361,"uid":77547,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"樓主係世澤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dea9c659d891331ba2de90c986b93e09d76af45","tid":2062361,"uid":87665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"356937786cdd9c60ac06ef751dd1bfbe39c10eaf","tid":2062361,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"你投稿去反駁佢囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T18:49:35.000Z","msg":"同意 咪公開反駁佢"},{"pid":"03df6f2a600cacfe4d005c8852ab9654c6b4bf98","tid":2062361,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"推"}]}